snippet.textDisplay:
I have a saltine hack for you:
Take 2 saltines
Smear on a layer of peanut butter on each
Now grind up some cannabis into a fine powder
Sprinkle cannabis on saltines
Sandwich saltines together
Wrap saltines in foil
Toss in oven at 420 degrees for 10 mins
Enjoy😇
snippet.textOriginal:

snippet.textDisplay: Crush those saltines up, add some salt, garlic powder, pepper and a favorite spice and bread some chicken cutlets with these saltines.  Wisk a couple eggs and some Parmesan cheese. Put the chicken in the freezer for half hour, this will make cutting easier. Then cut thin slices of chicken and pound the saltines into the chicken like a karate chop after dipping in the egg bath. You will tenderize them good and make nice flat cutlets. Then Fry them up and you got the best chicken cutlets now and for the next few days.
